name: 詹姆斯·保罗·格雷戈里
name_full: 詹姆斯·保罗·格雷戈里 James Paul Gregory
introduction: James Paul Gregory is an American actor.He is a graduate of San Francisco State University's School of Theatre and Dance.Since graduation, he has acted in a number of regional theatre productions and independent short films throughout the Bay Area.In addition to acting, Mr. Gregory is also a skilled singer, impressionist, and guitarist.He currently resides in Los Angeles, CA.
